#main-container.container-fluid
  .row
    .col-sm-12.col-md-4.col-md-push-1
      .row
        %img.col-sm-12#logo{:src => '/logo.jpg', :alt => 'Logo', :title => 'MAG Laboratory', :style => 'width: 100%;'}
      .row{:style => 'text-align: center; margin-top: 15px;'}
        %p
          %strong
            %a(href="mailto:contact@maglaboratory.org") contact@maglaboratory.org
        %p
          3960 Valley Blvd Unit G, Walnut, CA 91789
          %a(href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/MAG+Laboratory/@34.0390469,-117.8220769,18z/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x80c32c0f8edda7d9:0x56f9a6e0034a854" target="_blank") [Google Map]
        %p
          There are three entrances to Big Valley Industrial Park.
        %p
          The middle entrance has a 
          %a(href="#" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#sign-entrance") big sign.
        %p
          If you're driving southward, pass the sign and look for
          %a(href="#" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#flag-entrance") the flags.
          %br
          (It's the only one where you can turn left into it.)
          
    .col-sm-12.col-md-6.col-md-push-1{:style => 'margin-top: 10px;'}
      .container-fluid
        .row
          .col-sm-12
            %p
              We are a non-profit
              %a(href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hackerspace") hackerspace / makerspace
              and collaborative workspace based in Pomona, CA.
            %p
              People come to our space to work on projects, explore their inner artists, make cool gadgets, and interact with a community of like-minded individuals.
            %p
              Recent renovations partitioned out a sound-insulated presentation room, an electronics room and a machinery workshop. There are lazer cutters, 3d printers, a mill, a lathe, a drill press, a grinder, a jig saw, oscilloscopes, variable power supplies, a logic analyzer, soldering iron, heat gun, electronic components and more that this margin can't fit.
            %p
              We have a monthly open house on the last Saturday of every month and occasional public events and classes. Check the calendar below for our schedule and contact us if you're interested.
            %p
              We also have open project nights on Fridays from 7:30 PM to 10:00 PM. Work on your stuff. Share it. Inspire someone! Get inspired. They might even be interested in sharing some tricks and tips or lending a helping hand.
            %p
              Business meetings are Tuesdays from 7:30 PM to 8:30 PM and is open to the public. We tend to stay afterward to work on projects as well.

        .row
          .col-sm-12{:style => 'margin-top: 10px;'}
            %p
              Membership fees and donations pay the rent and bills. Check us out, and if you like what we do, join or donate to help us out. Thank you!
        .row
          .col-sm-12
            %div{:style => 'float: right;'}
              %a.btn.btn-primary(href="/membership") I want to be a Member!
            %div{:style => 'float: left;'}
              <form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"><input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick" /><input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="ZDGPLW6W5E9XJ" /><input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!" /><img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1" /></form>
            

.container-fluid{:style => 'margin-bottom: 50px;'}
  .row
    .col-sm-12
      <iframe src="https://www.google.com/calendar/embed?src=bjpkvaeg1rjq9u3c6utecq1jos%40group.calendar.google.com&amp;ctz=America/Los_Angeles" style="border: 0" width="100%" height="600" frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>
    .col-sm-12
      <iframe src="http://webchat.freenode.net?channels=%23MAGLaboratory" style="border: 1px solid black;margin-top:20px;" width="100%" height="600"></iframe>




#sign-entrance.modal.fade(role="dialog" aria-labeledby="signEntranceLabel")
  .modal-dialog.modal-lg
    .modal-content
      .modal-header
        %button.close(type="button" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close")
          %span(aria-hidden="true") &times;
        %h4.modal-title Big Valley Industrial Park sign
      .modal-body
        %img(src='/images/entrance-sign.png' alt="Big Valley Industrial Park sign" style="width:100%;height:auto;")
        %p This is the middle entrance. If you take this entrance, go all the way down, and then take a slight right until you see a triangular parking island with some palm trees. The space is right across from where parking island starts.
      .modal-footer
        %button.btn.btn-default(type="button" data-dismiss="modal") Close

#flag-entrance.modal.fade(role="dialog" aria-labelledby="flagEntranceLabel")
  .modal-dialog.modal-lg
    .modal-content
      .modal-header
        %button.close(type="button" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close")
          %span(aria-hidden="true") &times;
        %h4.modal-title Big Valley Industrial Entrance with Flags
      .modal-body
        %img(src="/images/entrance-flags.png" alt="Big Valley Industrial Entrance flags" style="width:100%;height:auto;")
        %p This is the only entrance where you can turn left to get in. So if you're heading south (I-10 behind you), then turn into here. You'll see the triangular parking island with palm trees. We're right across from where the long point of the island stops.
      .modal-footer
        %button.btn.btn-default(type="button" data-dismiss="modal") Close
